title: 3 BR/1.5 B $4,000 **UTILITIES INCLUDED!!**
posting_body: ['Apartment details:', '-Neighborhood: Ingleside', '-Bedrooms: 3', '-Bath: 1.5', '-Refrigerator', '-Oven + Stove', '-Granite kitchen countertops', '**Utilities Included!** (Water, electricity, garbage)', '-Laundromat conveniently located within half a mile', '-Rent: $4,000', 'Neighborhood Decription:', 'Welcome to 45 Randolph St!', 'Quietly located in a non-congested SF neighborhood, this middle floor corner apartment offers an ample and comfortable living space with many neighborhood amenities to cater to your daily needs.', 'This neighborhood is easily accessible both by car and public transit.', 'Right outside the front door, just 10 steps away is the M Muni train.', 'Also around the corner are both freeways I-280 North and South, less than a 2 minute drive away.', 'Neighborhood Amenities within 1 mile:', '-corner convenience store within 200 feet', '-cozy neighborhood coffee shop one block over', '-Stonestown Galleria Mall just minutes away via the Muni train right outside the front door', "-Trader Joe's", '-H Mart', '-Subway', '-Target', '- 2 Whole Foods locations', '-Retail shopping', '-Movie Theater inside Mall', '-24 Hour Fitness and City Sports Club gyms', '-Oceanview', 'Playground, Merced Heights playground, Cayuga Park, Minnie and Lovie recreational Center', 'This neighborhood can easily be considered a hidden gem- easily accessible, non congested, and comes with so many neighborhood amenities for your daily convenience.', 'Please call the number listed to come check it out and schedule a walk through appointment!', 'Contact: Oleg', 'show contact info']
